Reading.Wyomissing Hills, Pennsylvania:
Wyomissing Hills was a borough in Berks County, Pennsylvania, United States that merged into Wyomissing in January, 2002. The population was 2,568 at the 2000 census.


== Geography ==
Wyomissing Hills was located at 40º20'5" North, 75º58'54" West (40.334842, -75.981663).
